ABOUT KIONYX GFX

Kionyx GFX is a file downloader and extractor designed to handle large files, such as game assets or tools. To function properly, the app requires permission to manage all files on your device.

WHY THIS PERMISSION IS REQUIRED

The “Manage All Files” permission allows the app to:

- Download and save large files to locations you choose
- Extract ZIP or compressed files into selected folders
- Organize and manage files stored on your device

Without this permission, essential features like downloading, extracting, and file management may not work properly.

